---
import ChapterHead from "../ChapterHead.astro";
import ConclusionBox from "../ConclusionBox.astro";
---

<div
  id="conclusions"
  class="chapter h-full visible-page-width-disabled relative"
>
  <div class="absolute top-80 left-0">
    <span class="text-[100px] font-io-bold text-blue bg-orange"
      >CONCLUSIONS.</span
    >
  </div>
  <div class="relative left-[500px] h-full w-[1000px]">
    <ConclusionBox black={false} id={0} chapter="conclusions"
      ><span
        >Our assumptions about our primary stakeholders were not confirmed,
        actually they got flipped. We noticed during our testing that our
        primary stakeholders were less enthusiastic about being able to listen
        to voice memos from strangers than our secondary stakeholders.</span
      ></ConclusionBox
    >

    <ConclusionBox black={false} id={1} chapter="conclusions"
      ><span
        >Because we found out that our secondary stakeholders might be more
        interested in our product we should do more prototype testing with them.
      </span></ConclusionBox
    >

    <ConclusionBox black={false} id={2} chapter="conclusions"
      ><span
        >During testing we found out that there must be more work done on the
        iPad app flow. Not every tester was able to use the iPad interface
        without failures. We will test the interface more to find out where the
        exact problems are.
      </span></ConclusionBox
    >

    <ConclusionBox black={true} id={3} chapter="conclusions"
      ><span
        >Our app has a lot of potential, but we still need to do research on it
        to make sure the user will be satisfied.</span
      ></ConclusionBox
    >

    <ConclusionBox black={true} id={4} chapter="conclusions"
      ><span
        >We got the feedback of a tester that the house plant should have volume
        control.</span
      ></ConclusionBox
    >
    <ConclusionBox black={true} id={5} chapter="conclusions"
      ><span
        >A lot of people feel lonely sometimes and our tulip could bring a
        little happy moments in their lives.</span
      ></ConclusionBox
    >
  </div>
  <ChapterHead title="Conclusions." bottom={false} height={50} />
  <div class="w-[800px] absolute right-40 top-0" style="padding:52.73% 0 0 0;">
    <iframe
      src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/942721341?badge=0&autopause=0&player_id=0&app_id=58479"
      allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write"
      style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;"
      title="ux-research-tulips"></iframe>
  </div>
  <script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script>
</div>
<style>
  #conclusions {
    @apply min-w-[2500px];
  }
</style>
